lt;br&gt;[奶茶干杯]喜欢小泉八云、梦枕貘、京极夏彦的你，也一定会爱上镜花的日式唯美系怪谈！以他命名的“泉镜花文学奖”，更是助力日本文艺界历代名家：多和田叶子、森茉莉、吉本芭娜娜、横尾忠则、角田光代……&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;[奶茶干杯]收录芥川龙之介、三岛由纪夫长篇点评，译后记以长文详细梳理泉镜花其人其作，一册集结战国悲欢、江户风土、明治恋歌……真正贯彻日式古典美学的诡丽幻想谭！&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;三岛由纪夫说：“我敢断言，镜花生前无一知己。……我相信如今的时代正是重新评价镜花的好时机。”邀请大家和三岛一起来品味泉镜花的魅力。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/25094db80c007cd64e60d52acbf493b0571791768.png" width="1080" height="1440" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;img src="http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/344363bfa964eb63f5ce0110bdcebb1a571791768.png" width="1080" height="1440" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;img src="http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/2e5978c6eb2d007bfbd560a5b896f222571791768.png" width="1080" height="1440" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;img src="http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/222637286229196660838be5ce5f579c571791768.png" width="1080" height="1440" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;img src="http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/fe70e6a2172dd31c6c5ac43270203139571791768.png" width="1080" height="1440" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;img src="http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/04a0533a14dd2ad40fc92daec9df88cd571791768.png" width="1080" height="1440" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;img src="http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/578c489b1859a0f99d33edfc1d6f0bd6571791768.png" width="1080" height="1791" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;img src="http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/82bb90aa265656ca3ce34dca367645b3571791768.png" width="1080" height="1948" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;img src="http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/26a6550e44a5dc17ac086bc6c6ebf47d571791768.png" width="1080" height="1574" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt;图文地址：&lt;a href="https://www.bilibili.com/opus/1123989544059797511"&gt;https://www.bilibili.com/opus/1123989544059797511&lt;/a&gt;</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/opus/1123989544059797511</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/opus/1123989544059797511</guid><pubDate>Tue, 18 Nov 2025 02:28:11